@startuml vnpay_adapter_class_step06
title LeSonStore — Bước 6: Adapter VNPay

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

interface "PaymentGateway\n(contract)" as IGateway {
  +createPaymentUrl(params): Promise<string>
  +verifyCallback(query): { isSuccess, vnp_Params }
}

class "vnpayGateway.js\n<<Adapter>>" as Gateway {
  +createPaymentUrl(params)
  +verifyCallback(query)
}

class "vnpayService.js\n<<Adaptee>>" as Adaptee {
  +getPaymentUrl(params)
  +verifyReturnUrl(query)
  -sortObject()
  -HMAC SHA512
}

class "vnpayStrategy.js\n<<Client>>" as Strategy {
  +buildPaymentRedirect()
  +afterOrderCreated()
  +applySuccessfulReturn()
}

class "vnpayController.js" as Ctrl {
  +createPayment()
  +vnpayReturn()
}

cloud "VNPay API\n(sandbox / production)" as VNPay {
}

Strategy --> IGateway : uses
Ctrl --> IGateway : uses
Gateway ..|> IGateway : implements
Gateway --> Adaptee : adapts
Adaptee --> VNPay : redirect URL /\nreturn query

note right of Gateway
  Thin wrapper — không đổi HMAC
  Bước 2 tạo file; Bước 6 formalize
end note

@enduml
